item.title: Router Problem
item.dc:creator: @jme jme
item.description:
@jme wrote:

Does your connection work directly from the modem? If so, reset router to factory defaults and set it up appropriately.

Might be best off calling your isp for assistance but they might not help if its a router issue.

Be a little more specific and maybe we can help.
